ὖν","εἰμί"],"tr":"For if [we] may also live, we live to the lord; if [we] also may die, [we] die to the lord. Therefore, whether [we] may both live or whether [we] may also die, [we] are of the lord.","para":null,"para_continued":false,"words":[{"form":"ἐάν","lemma":"ἐάν","type":"conjunction","code":"C"},{"form":"τε","lemma":"τέ","type":"conjunction","code":"C"},{"form":"γὰρ","lemma":"γάρ","type":"conjunction","code":"C"},{"form":"ζῶμεν,","lemma":"ζάω","type":"verb","code":"V"},{"form":"τῷ","lemma":"ὁ","type":"article","code":"RA"},{"form":"κυρίῳ","lemma":"κύριος","type":"noun","code":"N"},{"form":"ζῶμεν,","lemma":"ζάω","type":"verb","code":"V"},{"form":"ἐάν","lemma":"ἐάν","type":"conjunction","code":"C"},{"form":"τε","lemma":"τέ","type":"conjunction","code":"C"},{"form":"ἀποθνῄσκωμεν,","lemma":"ἀποθνήσκω","type":"verb","code":"V"},{"form":"τῷ","lemma":"ὁ","type":"article","code":"RA"},{"form":"κυρίῳ","lemma":"κύριος","type":"noun","code":"N"},{"form":"ἀποθνῄσκομεν.","lemma":"ἀποθνήσκω","type":"verb","code":"V"},{"form":"ἐάν","lemma":"ἐάν","type":"conjunction","code":"C"},{"form":"τε","lemma":"τέ","type":"conjunction","code":"C"},{"form":"οὖν","lemma":"οὖν","type":"conjunction","code":"C"},{"form":"ζῶμεν","lemma":"ζάω","type":"verb","code":"V"},{"form":"ἐάν","lemma":"ἐάν","type":"conjunction","code":"C"},{"form":"τε","lemma":"τέ","type":"conjunction","code":"C"},{"form":"ἀποθνῄσκωμεν,","lemma":"ἀποθνήσκω","type":"verb","code":"V"},{"form":"τοῦ","lemma":"ὁ","type":"article","code":"RA"},{"form":"κυρίου","lemma":"κύριος","type":"noun","code":"N"},{"form":"ἐσμέν.","lemma":"εἰμί","type":"verb","code":"V"}]},{"v":9,"ref":"Rom 14:9","grc":"εἰς τοῦτο γὰρ ⸀Χριστὸς ⸀ἀπέθανεν καὶ ἔζησεν ἵνα καὶ νεκρῶν καὶ ζώντων κυριεύσῃ.","lemmas":["εἰς","οὗτος","γάρ","Χριστός","ἀποθνήσκω","καί","ζάω","ἵνα","νεκρός","κυριεύω"],"tr":"For into this Christ died and lived so that [he] might also rule over [the] dead and [the] living.","para":null,"para_continued":false,"words":[{"form":"εἰς","le